Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Software
Sub-Industry: Infrastructure Software
TaaSera, Inc. develops cloud based security solutions. The Company specializes in firewalls, intrusion detection, security event management, malware analysis, and endpoint security. TaaSera is based in California.




