	perimeter defenses that rely on threat information that is in constant flux, 
	to a behavior based risk intelligence that is resilient to evasion. TaaSera 
	is at the forefront of the technology that will revolutionize the IT 
	infection detection and response process.- 
	Scott Hartz

 

