Company Description


Taasera, Inc. is a privately-owned stealth mode startup founded by enterprise networking and security veterans with a track record of success and technology leadership in high-growth markets. They are singularly focused on making cloud computing trustworthy for enterprises.Traditional security solutions are ineffective against today's advanced malware and do not scale in virtual and cloud-based environments. Taasera provides a holistic, trust-based approach (trust-as-a-service) for visibility and control over private and public cloud infrastructure. Taasera can be deployed within minutes to provide continuous monitoring of data center resources, real-time correlation of system health events, and instantaneous remediation of compromised systems.




